creator: Jicksons Group
descriptionHtml:
Are you a Delivery company/Merchant?
Are you an Individual Delivery Driver? Then Worry no more because iFerch got you covered.
Sign up on our iFerch driver App to enjoy our amazing services, increase your daily sales and earnings as an individual rider to enable you meet your sales projection.
Are you a delivery Company? worry no more we got you covered too, we have a platform for you to enroll all your drivers, including your delivery Van, Motto Bikes, Cargo Car, Pick Up trucks, and guess what? It comes with company management panel to manage your Riders Movement and Payments, manual booking system to Assign task to your drivers manually.
Services: We will feed you with stream of customers who are wants their packages/parcels to be delivered in a single destination or multiple destinations just download the App and we will do the rest for you.
descriptionShort: Sign on with your Bike, car, van or kia trucks and make extra money delivering.
